        <updateDate>2019-08-26T21:04:14Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Combating Opioid Misuse Before Addiction for our Troops Act or the COMBAT Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to impose restrictions on opioid prescriptions provided under its pharmacy benefits program, including by limiting a first prescription to a seven-day supply. The bill provides exceptions for patients with certain conditions such as cancer. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
